Package: visTimeEvent
Type: Package
Title: Plotting time-to-event data 
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Katja Gutmair
Maintainer: The package maintainer <katja.gutmair@ibe.med.uni-muenchen.de>
Description: This package provides functions for visualizing time-to-event data 
            through Kaplan-Meier and cumulative incidence curves. 
            It supports calculating median time-to-event and event probabilities at specified 
            time points. Additionally, the package offers statistical tests for group 
            comparisons and can generate curves for both a single group and stratified by 
            multiple groups.
